---
description: WebOS architecture and repo structure rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repo implements a reusable website operating system starter, not a one-off site.
- Use Payload CMS + Next.js + TypeScript.
- Prefer generic naming for reusable content models and components.
- Keep Phase 1 limited to Home, About, Services, Contact.
- Keep the initial block system capped at 14 approved blocks.
- Favor server components and simple data flow.
- Avoid premature multi-tenant logic.
- If adding a new reusable pattern, document it in `docs/decisions.md`.
